"way\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"each dive\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"an unusual routine\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After each dive, the competitors exit the water and immediately take a shower, leaving many asking questions about the purpose of this, but the reality is the diver's muscles.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each dive\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitors\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"a shower\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"the purpose\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"the reality\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the diver's muscles\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts have said that the dive into the pool, and then getting out into the cold arena does not aid the muscles, and the hot shower is taken to keep muscles loose and reduce the chance of strains.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Experts\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"the dive\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the cold arena\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscles\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"the hot shower\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"muscles\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"strains\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Between each dive, those in the competition are often seen in a jacuzzi as they await their next one.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each dive\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"a jacuzzi\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diving is one of the most eye-catching events of the Olympics, and especially the swimming competition.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Diving\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"the most eye-catching events\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the swimming competition\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are eight Olympic diving events, the 3m springboard, individual, synchronised, men and women and the 10 m platform.\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight Olympic diving events\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dives are scored by a panel of judges who are looking at how aesthetically pleasing the movements are, the difficulty of the dive, and how well they enter the water.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The dives\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"a panel\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"the movements\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficulty\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"the dive\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While synchronised divers are also marked on how well the two competitors' movements are matched.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"synchronised divers\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"the two competitors' movements\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diving was first introduced in the 1904 Games in St Louis and has been at every one since then, while the women's competition was first introduced in 2012.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to